The value of `n` must be between 2 and 10^4 (inclusive).
The value of `threshold` must be between 0 and `n` (inclusive).
The length of `queries` must be between 1 and 10^5 (inclusive).
Each element in `queries` must be an array of length 2.
The values of `a_i` and `b_i` in each query must be between 1 and `n` (inclusive).
The values of `a_i` and `b_i` in each query must be different.
